1. Created project
2. Create package -> com.java.class01
3. Creat class

What are the components of class?

1)Documentatin
2)*Package declaration
3)Import section
4)*Class declaration
5)*Main method

**Java will execute code from top to bottom and left to right

Rules of Identifier

1) Allowed char is 0-9, a-z, $, _
2) You cannot start identifier name with digit - Invalid names: 1stNum, 1num
3) Identifiers name are case sensitive
4) We can't use keywords reserved by Java as identifier

Some examples:

abc123	- valid
_a_	- valid
$$$	- valid
num 1	- invalid
_1num_	- valid
num_1	- valid


int, long, short, byte	- whole number


byte is 8 bit so (-128) -> (127) only
2^8 = 256










